title: Make it Count - Switzerland 2015
description:
Congrats to OLIVER WEISMANTEL who won the MAKE IT COUNT contest in Zurich, Switzerland !
Oliver won a spot in the European Finals that will take place in Bolzano, Italy, and a chance to win a trip to California to compete for Element sponsorship at Nyjah's park!

More info : elementmakeitcount.com

OVERALL WINNER
Oliver Weismantel

results : 

14 TO 16 : 
1. Niko Feratovic
2. Lamin
3. Glen Schönbächler

17 & UP : 
1/ Oliver Weismantel
2/ Simon Perrottet
3/ Sämi Nigg
